{"tid":2257733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［傳媒譯名］香港傳媒（包括但不限於CCTVB）對馬來西亞政治人物譯名永遠唔跟當地華人/華文傳媒","createTime":"2020-10-25T12:26:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T13:35:12.000Z","uid":53673,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9016ea998618f45bec677079d97a8f84bd26f923","tid":2257733,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:26:01.000Z","msg":"我同意每人都可以有自己譯法<br />\n純粹想知點解香港傳媒死都唔跟<br />\n係咪有咩特別原因？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMalaysia Prime Minister<br />\n大馬華文傳媒：馬來西亞首相<br />\n香港傳媒：馬來西亞總理<br />\n（但英國首相、日本首相又唔譯人地做英國總理、日本總理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNajib<br />\n大馬華文傳媒：納吉<br />\n香港傳媒：納吉<span class=\"red\">布</span> <br />\n（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現任阿公<br />\n大馬華文傳媒：阿都拉<br />\n香港傳媒：阿<span class=\"red\">卜</span>杜拉<br />\n（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"4a3ba77ce9b70bf8e0c5861bad1c055929c6ba5c","tid":2257733,"uid":53673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"Mahathir<br />\n大馬華文傳媒：馬哈迪<br />\n香港傳媒：馬哈<span class=\"red\">蒂爾</span> <br />\n（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"5df498168f3abaa0849671a056b851c4ba4f856a","tid":2257733,"uid":18604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:45:49.000Z","msg":"香港啲傳媒而家好多走去跟新華社<br />\n咩弗吉尼亞嗰啲都係大陸人手筆"},{"pid":"6c05891551305b88c2ffa6e12a926ebb5751a2bb","tid":2257733,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:49:46.000Z","msg":"Prime Minister 呢個可圈可點，加拿大澳洲有英女皇，咪又係照叫總理<br />\n<br />\n各處各鄉村各處例，香港比較冇統一譯名，所以有陣時係會比較亂<i